by Tobion at 2015-07-01T16:00:05Z

It cannot be empty because it uses the default timezone if none is provided: https://github.com/zhil/symfony/blob/2.8/src/Symfony/Component/Form/Extension/Core/DataTransformer/BaseDateTimeTransformer.php#L51
So you don't need to check it (an invalid one would fail before as well).

